annotation.text:
Be sure to read the Wackypedia page and/or [http://musicbrainz.org/artist/73e0693d-dbf0-45e8-ba86-e1ab0897db31.html|Norman Granz] notes to learn more about JATP.

Now, in a number of occasions, sleeves of releases containing JATP material used the somewhat fictitious artist name "JATP", or "Jazz at the Philharmonic", or "Jazz at the Philharmonic All-Stars" to credit tracks where the whole lot of artists featuring in the event were jamming altogether.

As such, this artist entry refer to a wide variety of settings and a wide range of musicians and styles.
It's not a group, so please don't add membership / collaboration relationships to other artists, but rather use performance ARs to individually credit each relevant track.
